								<h2 id="t_549c1d970102yyos" class="titName SG_txta">我和共和国的故事：两场战争让我印象深刻落后就要挨打是切肤之痛</h2>
			
					<span class="time SG_txtc">(2019-10-01 14:45:39)</span><div class="turnBoxzz"><a href="javascript:;" class="SG_aBtn SG_aBtn_ico SG_turn"  action-type="reblog" action-data="{srcBlog:1, blogId:'549c1d970102yyos'}"><cite><img class="SG_icon SG_icon111" src="http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" width="15" height="15" align="absmiddle">转载<em class="arrow">▼</em></cite></a></div>		</div>
		<div class="articalTag" id="sina_keyword_ad_area">
			<table>
				<tr>
					<td class="blog_tag">
